bagaimana ibumu meninggal?

135
00:10:50,087 --> 00:10:52,496
Dia menderita penyakit jantung.

136
00:10:52,496 --> 00:10:55,294
Kardiomiopati dilatasi.

137
00:10:58,198 --> 00:11:02,788
